trans-unit.source: The MsmqTransportSecurity class encapsulates the transport security settings for queued transports.
trans-unit.target: MsmqTransportSecurity 클래스에는 대기 중된 전송 위한 전송 보안 설정을 캡슐화합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class, using an existing instance.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"> </xref> 클래스, 기존 인스턴스를 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The existing instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class, to be used in initializing the new instance.
trans-unit.target: 기존 인스턴스는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"> </xref> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화 하는 데 사용할 합니다.

trans-unit.source: other is .
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode"></xref> that is associated with this instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 가져오거나는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode"> </xref> 의이 인스턴스와 연결 된는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can authenticate messages that are sent to message queues that require authentication, or messages can explicitly request authentication.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ 인증을 사용 해야 하는 메시지 큐에 전송 된 메시지를 인증할 수 또는 메시지 인증을 명시적으로 요청할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The default authentication mode is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode>.
The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode"></xref> that is associated with this instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
The value is not one of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode"></xref> values.
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm"></xref> that is associated with this instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 가져오거나는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm"> </xref> 의이 인스턴스와 연결 된는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: MSMQ can encrypt messages on the wire when transferring messages between message queue managers.
trans-unit.target: MSMQ는 메시지 큐 관리자 간에 메시지를 전송할 때 통신 중에 메시지를 암호화할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The default encryption algorithm is <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm>.
The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm"></xref> that is associated with this instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
The value is not one of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm"></xref> values.
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel"></xref> that is associated with this instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 가져오거나는 <xref href="System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel"> </xref> 의이 인스턴스와 연결 된는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The default protection level is <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel>.
The <xref href="System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel"></xref> that is associated with this instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
The value is not one of the <xref href="System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel"></xref> values.
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm"></xref> that is associated with this instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity"></xref> class.
